### Applicability (Level 2)

This objective applies to all apps in which clients will enter sensitiive information into their app or browser.

### Guidelines for developers

All sensitive data entered into forms must be sanitized from the client side as soon as the form is submitted.  Ideally, the data should be overwritten with zeros or random bits.
